---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Workflow map | ThunderBayAI" description="Request a local workflow map to identify operational bottlenecks, manual admin, and follow-up gaps in your Thunder Bay business.">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container split-panel">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <p class="eyebrow">Workflow CTA</p>
        <h1>Request a local workflow map.</h1>
        <p class="lead">If your business depends on fast lead handling, clean handoffs, and fewer dropped opportunities, a workflow map is often the fastest way to see what needs to change first.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a class="button" href="https://frayze.ca/contact/">Request the Workflow Map</a>
          <a class="button secondary" href="/thunder-bay-ai-automation">See AI automation pathway</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <p class="eyebrow">Best fit</p>
        <ul class="check-list">
          <li>contractors with missed-call problems</li>
          <li>service businesses with weak pipeline visibility</li>
          <li>teams buried in manual admin and follow-up</li>
          <li>owners who need implementation clarity before buying tools</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
